title: Speak Now
body:
Inspired by Taylor Swift’s “Speak Now”.

Speak Now

I am not the kind of girl,Who should be rudely barging in on a white veil occasion.I shouldn’t do it. I shouldn’t be sneaking into your wedding; but I do.Making my way through the guests on the green…

body:
Guys,

so today me and my boyfriend were watching the speak now tour live and during it he goes “I hope she plays all too well”. (I know he’s a keeper right! 💗)

And I laughed and told him that unfortunately it didn’t exist yet. And then he goes “wow a world without all too well…”

And that it me SO HARD. like that thought had never crossed my mind before

A WORLD WITHOUT ALL TOO WELL IS A WORLD I DONT WANT TO BE IN

HOW DID WE SURVIVE BEFORE??
